title: S12 Ep139: Our Occulted History with Jim Marrs
itunes:title: Our Occulted History with Jim Marrs
description:
Jim Marrs joins us to talk about the Alien Agenda and the explosion of the Space X rockets, among other conspiracy theories...

Dave & Tim pay their respects to the legendary Jim Marrs with a replay of his final visit with us from last year.
